room_title: Escape room "The Hangover" by Escape the Place in Colorado Springs
room_description: You and your friends partied a little too hard last night. You woke up and soon realized you are locked in a hotel room and have no idea how to get out. You have no recollection of how you got here and why is the door locked. Piece together the events of last night, find the key, and escape the room.
